regions.title: Cluster of toothbrushes in cup
regions.description: This region contains the heads and handles of several toothbrushes protruding from a cup, as well as a portion of toothpaste visible among them.

summary: All identified cells form a single connected region representing the cluster of toothbrushes in the cup. No cells were removed, as each contains part of a toothbrush or is strongly connected to high-confidence detections.
